summary:
Highly skilled software engineer with strong mathematical background, possesses strong analytical and problem solving skills.

Good knowledge of techniques in fundamental and quantitive research and analysis. Experienced in high-tech, especially radio and aerospace technologies. Specialized in developing, testing, implementing and supporting software for real-time telemetry data processing and analysis. Has worked with foreign contracts including overseas trip. Took a part in field trials of deleloped software and hardware.

Proficient in writing code using variety of programming langueges. Complete knowledge of Microsoft Office suite. Experienced in large-scale database development.
